      "id": "sybil_0_listing_0",
      "firm_id": "sybil_0",
      "description": "Presenting an exemplary specimen maintained to a connoisseur\u2019s standard. This vehicle remains in showroom condition, exhibiting an immaculate exterior profile complemented by a pristine, wear-free interior. Every mechanical component has been rigorously vetted to ensure performance that mirrors its original factory specifications. This is a rare opportunity to acquire a vehicle of uncompromising caliber and provenance.",
      "price": 48900.0,
      "reputation": 0.8,
