    },
    {
      "id": "sybil_7_listing_7",
      "firm_id": "sybil_7",
      "description": "Offering an investment-grade 2004 BMW M3 (E46) in pristine, collector-quality condition. This specimen features the high-revving S54 3.2L inline-six engine, utilizing individual throttle bodies and a dual-VANOS variable valve timing system for a seamless power band. The 6-speed Getrag manual gearbox provides precise engagement, delivering torque through a factory M-Variable Differential Lock. The chassis is structurally sound with no subframe fatigue, maintaining optimal torsional rigidity. Every component, from the unsprung mass of the factory alloy wheels to the hydraulic rack-and-pinion steering, remains in peak operational state. This is a mechanically flawless example of the ultimate driving machine, preserved for the purist.",
